title: Skin Trade 003 (2013) (4 Covers) (Darkness-Empire).cbr
description:
Werewolves clash with snarling ferocity but Randi Wade is on the cusp of uncovering a trail of murders that ends with her father's death years ago. A chess game is being played with humans as the pieces and life and death the stakes. She must navigate the mysterious machinations before she becomes the latest victim of brutal murder. GEORGE RR MARTIN's World Fantasy Award winning story, Skin Trade, delivers a mix of intense horror and fascinating character drama.

Available with Regular, Wraparound, Grisly and Skinned Retailer Incentive covers by series artist Mike Wolfer.
